Hardware requirement:
    1) CPU: at least 4 cores
    2) Menory: at least 16 GB
    3) Disk: at least 100 GB
All of those based on the configuration, and the more the better.

Software requirement:
    VirtualBox 6.1: the VM we released has been tested in VirtualBox 6.1
    or Ubuntu 20.04: the build instructions for the project has been tested in Ubuntu 20.04
